This position under the Volunteer Resource Optimisation team will be involved in our major professional capability development programme - Volunteer Management Masterclass Learning Event (working title) scheduled for Jan 2021.&nbsp; The trainee will :

- conceptualise and research on the scope of the masterclass topic as well as the conduct of the whole learning event
- liaise with the speakers (local and overseas) on their delivery (eg engagement terms and contract, materials)
- work with multiple partners (including funders) on the implementation of this event
- work with the comms team on the design and outreach (marketing) of this event to the sector and to ensure there's take-up rate of the programmes under this event
- manage actual day operation of the whole event with venue and event partner
- compilation of post-event learning and evaluation reports